videoScrapeInstance.title: Intro to MacBook Pro (and iLife '06)
videoScrapeInstance.description: Watch Peter and I walkthrough the features of the MacBook Pro with an Apple representative. Note that  Apple only had prototype units for the expo. In this video, watch for: - Real-time performance of various apps - How the breakaway magnetic power plug works - Overview of the Mac's ports, including Expresscard 34 slot - How the built-in iSight works - How the Apple Remote is Mac-assignable
